Name "Chamber Automation"

-- ============================================
-- Generic Chamber Processor
-- Takes any 9 items from barrel, sends to chambers,
-- extracts source_gem outputs back to barrel
-- ============================================
Every 20 ticks do
    Input 9 item:: from Barrel
    Output item:: to each Chamber top side
    Input item::source_gem from each Chamber bottom side
    Output item:: to Barrel
End
